description:
The file 'EMG-ANN-Data.txt' comprises six columns of experimental data:&nbsp; 
 1. Timing records obtained from the EMG measurement device (s). 2. Electromyographic data, filtered to remove noise (micro-Volts). 3, 4, 5, 6. The four outputs of the deep artificial neural network are represented in a binary numerical base as (y3, y2, y1, y0). 
 Data represent recognition of twelve upper limbs muscular gestures.

